{"tid":189111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 大劉被判囚5年3個月","createTime":"2017-04-06T08:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T18:02:33.000Z","uid":36995,"like":93,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"95b84220d29aa1d0bddce453ebd898bff3a76c8a","tid":189111,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"華人置業前主席劉鑾雄及本港商人羅傑承，因涉嫌以2,000萬元賄賂歐文龍，以獲取澳門樓盤「御海‧南灣」5幅土地批給的案件，繼澳門終審法院早前駁回劉鑾雄的上訴後，終審法院周五再裁定劉鑾雄提出的統一司法見解無效，爭辯理由不成立，意味着劉鑾雄須監禁5年3個月的判決，基本上已是塵埃落定。<br />\n<br />\n華人置業前主席劉鑾雄及本港商人羅傑承，因涉嫌以2,000萬元賄賂歐文龍，以獲取澳門樓盤「御海‧南灣」5幅土地批給，早前被澳門初級法院判行賄及洗黑錢罪成，各判囚5年3個月。2人其後向澳門中級法院提出上訴被駁回。終審法院早前再駁回劉鑾雄提出統一司法見解的「非常上訴」。<br />\n<br />\n劉鑾雄周五如常到灣仔午膳，用膳後離開時，只一直「頭耷耷」，未有回應任何提問。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.next.nextmedia.com/images/next-photos/NextMag/1229/640pixfolder/N1229_022_Jerry_130920_8270.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.next.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2FNextMag%2F1229%2F640pixfolder%2FN1229_022_Jerry_130920_8270.jpg&h=42e66140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160305/mobile/bkn-20160305000343319-0305_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160305%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20160305000343319-0305_00822_001.html&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=1d74d08a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160305/mobile/bkn-20160305000343319-0305_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n通緝犯教廢青做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bd927037e76c69ded019178d809521de5ee357","tid":189111,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T08:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2e2a5ea5b46f05a21c0d214c1c0b9dedfbea16","tid":189111,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi